    <h2>Getting Started</h2>

    <p>Ready to jump into Fortnite? Follow these steps:</p>

    <ol>
        <li>Download and install Fortnite from the official <a href="https://www.epicgames.com/fortnite/en-US/download">Fortnite website</a>.</li>
        <li>Create an Epic Games account and customize your character.</li>
        <li>Drop into the battle, build structures, and achieve victory!</li>
    </ol>

    <p>For tips, strategies, and community discussions, visit the <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/FortNiteBR/">Fortnite subreddit</a>.</p>

    <p>Join the Fortnite community and embark on an epic journey filled with battles, building, and boundless creativity!</p>

